HEADWORD: Uncurrent
<hw>Un*cur"rent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not current.
Specifically: Not passing in common payment; not receivable at par or
full value; <as>as, <ex>uncurrent</ex> notes</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

